descript.abstract: This data displays the boundaries of countries surrounding Indonesia and was prepared by WRI for use in the Interactive Atlas of Indonesia's Forests (2009). It was derived from the ESRI dataset named "Countries 2006" (ESRI Data and Maps, 2006). The World Resources Institute modified the boundaries of the countries bordering Indonesia slightly to fit with the boundaries of Indonesia, using the national boundaries data produced by Badan Pusat Statistik (BPS), the institution in charged of producing the Statistics of The Republic of Indonesia, in 2003.
descript.supplinf: This data was made only for mapping and rendering purposes for this Atlas.
